---
import "../styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Newsletter from "../components/Newsletter.astro";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle="About">
  <div class="top-section">
    <div class="top-text">
      <p class="text-2xl px-4 md:mt-0 mt-8 has-large-font-size">
        I'm a web development consultant and educator working with people around
        the world from Northern Ireland.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img
        width="200"
        height="200"
        decoding="async"
        loading="lazy"
        src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
        alt=""
        class="wp-post-366 wp-image-388 size-full"
        data-public-id="face-1.jpg"
        data-format="jpg"
        data-transformations="f_auto,q_auto"
        data-version="1620142072"
        data-size="1280 1280"
        data-srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/w_300,h_300,c_fill/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/w_1024,h_1024,c_fill/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/w_150,h_150,c_fill/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/w_768,h_768,c_fill/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 768w"
        data-sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"
        srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/w_300,h_300,c_fill/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/w_1024,h_1024,c_fill/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/w_150,h_150,c_fill/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/kc-cloud/images/w_768,h_768,c_fill/f_auto,q_auto/v1620142072/face-1/face-1.jpg?_i=AA 768w"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    I started coding at 8 on my Spectrum 128k and have been attached to a
    computer ever since.
  </p>

  <p>
    As a secondary school Maths teacher, I spent a decade making complex topics
    accessible. I used code to help my students in their learning and to speed
    up my own administration tasks.
  </p>

  <p>
    I migrated to being a web developer and worked with clients from Sega to the
    British Library to small, emerging start-ups.
  </p>

  <p>
    Now, I primarily teach development in a variety of live and pre-recorded
    ways.
  </p>

  <p>
    I write and produce written and video content to help developers continually
    level up and not get stuck in “tutorial hell”.
  </p>

  <p>
    <a href="/courses">I run workshops and training</a> to allow teams and
    individuals to rapidly upskill in new frameworks and approaches. I offer
    <a href="/mentoring" data-type="URL" data-id="/mentoring"
      >1:1 mentoring and coaching</a
    > for developers looking for help taking their journey to the next level.
  </p>

  <p>
    I also tweet, so <a
      href="https://twitter.com/dolearning"
      data-type="URL"
      data-id="https://twitter.com/dolearning">come follow me on Twitter</a
    >.
  </p>

  <h2>Podcasts and Interview with me</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="https://makelifeworkpodcast.com/kevin-cunningham/"
        >Make Life Work with Kevin Cunningham</a
      >
    </li><li>
      <a
        href="https://landingintech.com/episodes/ep5-kevin-cunningham-from-maths-to-fullstack/"
        >From teaching math to becoming a fullstack developer</a
      >
    </li><li>
      <a href="https://learnetto.com/blog/kevin-cunningham-headless-wordpress"
        >Interview with Kevin Cunningham on software development, teaching and
        headless WordPress</a
      >
    </li><li>
      <a
        href="https://egghead-io-course-notes.simplecast.com/episodes/wordpress-as-a-headless-content-management-system-cms-and-graphql-api-with-kevin-cunningham?share=true"
        >WordPress as a Headless Content Management System (CMS) and GraphQL API
        with Kevin Cunningham</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p><em>Reach out if you think I might be a good fit for your podcast.</em></p>
  <Newsletter />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .top-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-direction: column-reverse;
  }
  .top-text {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 8px;
    line-height: 0;
  }

  a:hover {
    color: #f56565;
  }
  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .top-section {
      flex-direction: row;
    }
  }
</style>
